ActCanadian Space Agency Act
SubjectMOU with Alberta re: Canadian Space Program
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Industry and the Minister Responsible for the Canadian Space Agency to enter into a Memorandum of Understanding with the Ministry of Education of Alberta for the purpose of carrying out collaborative activities to encourage increased scientific literacy among educators and students in Alberta through increased access to CANADIAN SPACE PROGRAM learning content and professional development opportunities. This agreement is for a term of 3 years and entered into force on September 23, 2009.
